  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
  <ext_description linkend="Activity_method_implementation_arm.Activity_method_realization">
	  An <b>Activity_method_realization</b> is  a further specification of how an 
	  activity method is to be performed with the 
	  <express_ref linkend="activity_method:arm:Activity_method_arm.Activity_method"/>.
	  <note number="1">
		More than one specification can be associated with the same <express_ref
linkend="activity_method:arm:Activity_method_arm.Activity_method"/>. 
	</note>
	<example>
		For a given planned activity there may be a task specification, a statement of how task performance is 
		to be logged and a schedule that all apply.
	</example>
</ext_description>

